parameters.name: 町・村っぽい感じ（夜っぽい）

parameters:
\n<Ameria>"We're almost at Anatos. I guess tonight will be our last
time camping out."
\n<Lyric>"You hate the dark, so that must be a relief, right?"

\n<Ameria>"Yeah... But I'll miss sitting around the fire with everyone
a little bit."

\n<Ameria>"I've always been with my sister and the priest. So
traveling with friends like this feels so fresh and really
fun."
Roselitte and Lyric looked at each other--
\n<Ameria>"Eh, eh? What? Did I say something weird?"
\n<Roselitte>"No, not at all. We're talking about something else."
\n<Ameria>"Ehh-! ...Don't tell me, I'm being left out..."
\n<Lyric>"...Hey, can we talk for a bit?"
\n<Lyric>"About when I tried to have Begi-Ade grant my wish."

\n<Ameria>"...You don't have to force yourself to talk about it if you
don't want to."

\n<Lyric>"Yeah. Well, actually, it's not that big of a deal.... I
just want to talk about it a little. That's all."

\n<Lyric>"...My mother. My mother was killed by a knight right in
front of me."

\n<Lyric>"It happened when we were living in a cave together.
Suddenly knights stormed in and stabbed my mother just like
that."

\n<Lyric>"Yeah. But it's okay. He wasn't a knight from the Valam
Empire."
\n<Lyric>"See. It's not such a big deal, is it?"
\n<Lyric>"...Begi-Ade wanted to devour that knight's lust."

\n<Lyric>"So he approached me, who held a grudge against the knight,
and promised to grant my wish in exchange for feeding him
the knight's lust."
\n<Lyric>"...My wish. It was to bring my mother back to life."

\n<Lyric>"To resurrect my mother, I went after humans other than the
knight, involved many innocent people, and in the end, tried
to forcefully bring down the knight."

\n<Lyric>"...But in the end, far from bringing my mother back to
life, I was killed by that knight. Really, serves me right,
huh?"

\n<Ameria>"Tha... That's not true. After all, Lyric was told by Begi-
Ade..."
Lyric shook her head in response.
\n<Lyric>"I'm not as kind as you are."

\n<Lyric>"There are people who got hurt because of me. People who
died... At first, I didn't care what happened to humans."

\n<Lyric>"But after tasting death once... causing all that trouble, I
was revived..."
\n<Lyric>"Being with you all... as time passed..."

\n<Lyric>"I've come to think that if I wish for something, I might
hurt someone again..."

\n<Lyric>"Now, whatever I do... even just thinking about it... it's a
little scary."
\n<Lyric>"...I regret what happened in the past."

\n<Lyric>"But there's a part of me that still wants to rely on Begi-
Ade again."

\n<Lyric>"...That's why. That's why I want to turn Begi-Ade to
ashes."

\n<Lyric>"I want to meet him, find out why I was revived and
everything, and then erase Begi-Ade from this world."

\n<Lyric>"Unless I get rid of him, I probably won't be able to move
forward."
\n<Lyric>"I want you to lend me your strength."
\n<Lyric>"...The dead do not come back to life."
\n<Roselitte>"Are you planning to strike at my sleeping throat... fua..."
Lyric lay down next to Roselitte.
\n<Roselitte>"Infidelity is not something to be praised, is it?"

\n<Lyric>"Nfufu. You've started to say things like that too, haven't
you?"

\n<Lyric>"...Hey. It's not something to talk about when going to
sleep but,"
\n<Lyric>"How many humans and demons have you killed up until now?"

\n<Roselitte>"...It's really not something to talk about when going to
sleep."
\n<Lyric>"It's been bothering me so much I can't sleep."
\n<Roselitte>"Even if you ask that, it won't provide any comfort."

\n<Roselitte>"The fact that you tried to bring your mother back to life,
and as a result, many victims were made..."

\n<Roselitte>"I won't tell you not to worry. However, I think there's no
need for you to dwell on it so much."
\n<Roselitte>"After all, that's just how the world is."
\n<Roselitte>"...Ameria is a strong girl, isn't she?"

\n<Roselitte>"She possesses not only the power to fight but also the
power to heal those who are wounded and a kind heart."

\n<Roselitte>"Being called her friend makes me feel a bit scared. I
wonder if it's okay to be myself like this."
\n<Roselitte>"...But it's okay. You can be Ameria's friend."

\n<Roselitte>"Because you are also a strong and kind child, just like
Ameria."

\n<Roselitte>"...Still, if you feel absolutely pulled by the past and
lack the confidence to stay with her..."
\n<Roselitte>"And if there is someone who stands in your way..."
\n<Lyric>"...You've said everything I wanted to hear. You pass."

\n<Lyric>"Rose, just one more push. With just one more push, my heart
will fall for you."
Roselitte brought her mouth close to Lyric's ear.
